808
00:53:40,150 --> 00:53:42,276
味道很好
It's good.

809
00:53:42,444 --> 00:53:44,069
要不要來點牛排 你喜歡牛排吧？
What about some steak? You want steak?

810
00:53:44,237 --> 00:53:45,738
- 嗯 - 這，來點牛排
- Mmm. - Here, have some steak.

811
00:53:45,905 --> 00:53:48,032
這一大塊都是你的
Here's a big piece for you.

812
00:53:48,199 --> 00:53:50,326
給你
There you go.

813
00:53:54,039 --> 00:53:55,497
不錯，哈？
Good, huh?

814
00:54:04,883 --> 00:54:07,593
你到底因為什麼進來的？
What'd you do to get in here, anyways?

815
00:54:09,804 --> 00:54:12,097
我做了我應該做的事
I did what I had to do.

816
00:54:17,312 --> 00:54:19,521
你搞了個妞還是什麼？
So you got a girl or something?

817
00:54:22,025 --> 00:54:24,902
嗯，說來話長
Mmm, it's a long story.

818
00:54:28,907 --> 00:54:30,783
駕駛員，還要多久？
Pilot, how much longer?

819
00:54:30,950 --> 00:54:34,036
預計時間兩分鐘
Two minutes.

820
00:54:36,873 --> 00:54:39,291
你呢？搞了個妞？
How about you? You have a girl?

821
00:54:39,459 --> 00:54:41,960
- 在家裡搞了好幾個妞 - 哦，是嗎？
- Got a few girls back home. - Oh, yeah?

822
00:54:42,128 --> 00:54:43,796
是的
Yeah.

823
00:54:43,963 --> 00:54:46,965
- 你在這沒有男朋友吧？ - 滾蛋吧
- You have a boyfriend in here or no? - Get the fuck out of here.

824
00:55:01,189 --> 00:55:03,023
這是，這是雷諾斯的
This is- it's Reynolds's.

825
00:55:04,150 --> 00:55:06,527
- 看來情況不妙 - 快挖
- Not a good sign, Nick. - Just dig.

826
00:55:20,542 --> 00:55:22,376
- 上帝！ - 雷諾斯
- Jesus Christ! - Reynolds!

827
00:55:22,544 --> 00:55:25,587
- 他失去意識了 - 雷諾斯
- He's unconscious. - Reynolds!

828
00:55:25,755 --> 00:55:28,757
他死了，尼克 他死了
He's gone, Nick. He's gone.

829
00:55:28,925 --> 00:55:30,968
氧氣罩？
- Oxygen? - Get something to get him out!

830
00:55:31,136 --> 00:55:34,756
- 找東西把他弄出來 
Detective: He's got IV lines going to his-

831
00:55:34,806 --> 00:55:37,050
他把他銬住了
He's got him cuffed!

832
00:55:37,100 --> 00:55:42,222
你有開手銬的鑰匙嗎？
Nick: Listen, you got your keys to the cuffs?

833
00:55:42,272 --> 00:55:44,641
- 嗯！ - 嗯！
- Mmm! - Mmm.

834
00:55:44,691 --> 00:55:46,400
媽的
Shit.

835
00:55:46,568 --> 00:55:49,236
哦，上帝，吃的真爽
Oh, God, I'm so happy.

836
00:55:49,404 --> 00:55:51,905
你的幸運日，啊？ 有東西吃
Your lucky day, huh? Get some food.

837
00:55:52,073 --> 00:55:54,950
這裡，要拍張照嗎？
Here, wanna take a shot at this?

838
00:55:55,118 --> 00:55:57,244
- 這是什麼？ - 知道怎麼用嗎？
- What is it? - Know how to use it?

839
00:55:57,412 --> 00:55:59,663
不知道
No.

840
00:56:16,431 --> 00:56:19,308
哦，該死，快看
Inmate: Oh, shit! Check this out!

841
00:56:22,395 --> 00:56:24,646
他瘋了
He's crazy!

842
00:56:24,814 --> 00:56:26,315
現在別停下，夥計
Don't stop now, partner!

843
00:56:26,483 --> 00:56:29,318
幹掉他，快！ 把他頭割下來
Finish him, come on! Take his head off!

844
00:56:29,486 --> 00:56:33,739
割下來
Take it off!

845
00:57:03,561 --> 00:57:05,938
我需要洗個澡，典獄長
I need a shower, Warden.

846
00:57:06,105 --> 00:57:07,314
把他弄出去
Get him out of there!

847
00:57:10,860 --> 00:57:13,320
唐尼根，你的表幾點了？
Nick: Dunnigan, what time do you have?

848
00:57:15,573 --> 00:57:16,865
1點37分
37.

849
00:57:17,033 --> 00:57:18,825
到這裡我們大約花了15分鐘
Took us roughly 15 minutes to get here.

850
00:57:18,993 --> 00:57:20,077
是嗎？
Yeah?

851
00:57:20,245 --> 00:57:22,746
雷諾斯的氧氣被設定在1點15分關閉
Reynolds's air was rigged to shut off at 1:15.

852
00:57:22,914 --> 00:57:25,666
如果謝爾頓能準時吃到午餐 他應該能活著
If Shelton would have got his lunch on time, he'd still be alive.

853
00:57:25,833 --> 00:57:27,125
去他媽的，尼克
Fuck this guy, Nick.

854
00:57:27,293 --> 00:57:31,046
他想要玩遊戲 我們也可以跟他玩
He wants to play games, we can play games too.

855
00:57:31,214 --> 00:57:33,549
我們得把手套摘下來
We need to take the gloves off.

856
00:57:33,716 --> 00:57:35,425
不行
No.

857
00:57:39,556 --> 00:57:42,599
尼克，我是莎拉 聽著，克萊德殺了他的牢友
Nick, it's Sarah. Listen, Clyde murdered his cell-mate.

858
00:57:42,767 --> 00:57:46,645
典獄長大發雷霆，要把他移至禁閉室
The warden is furious. He's moving him to solitary.

859
00:57:46,813 --> 00:57:49,064
目前我就只知道這些
That's all I know right now.

860
00:58:19,929 --> 00:58:22,764
目前什麼情況？
How are we doing?

861
00:58:22,932 --> 00:58:25,851
不錯，你能相信嗎？
Great. Can you believe this?

862
00:58:26,019 --> 00:58:29,146
把他iPod拆了找線索
Checking his iPod for clues.

863
00:58:29,314 --> 00:58:30,856
我對我女兒也這麼做
I do the same thing with my daughter's.

864
00:58:31,024 --> 00:58:32,733
有收穫嗎？
Learn anything?

865
00:58:32,900 --> 00:58:35,319
恩，他們都聽垃圾音樂
Yeah, they both got shit taste in music.

866
00:58:37,363 --> 00:58:39,740
我們有招術跟這個傢伙玩了嗎？
We got a game plan with this guy or what?

867
00:58:39,907 --> 00:58:41,491
招術？
Game plan?

868
00:58:41,659 --> 00:58:43,535
我跟你說，我有個招術
I tell you, I got a game plan.

869
00:58:43,703 --> 00:58:46,413
給我跟他五分鐘時間 我會搞殘這個混蛋
Give me five minutes alone with him and I'll cripple the fucker.

870
00:58:46,581 --> 00:58:49,583
我才不管他家庭發生了什麼
I don't give a shit what happened to his family.

871
00:58:49,751 --> 00:58:51,209
沒有借口
It's no excuse.

872
00:58:58,301 --> 00:58:59,885
哇
Wow.

873
00:59:07,018 --> 00:59:08,685
就在這
Stop right there.

874
00:59:17,362 --> 00:59:19,071
進屋去
Step into the cell.

875
01:00:05,284 --> 01:00:07,746
我們發現雷諾斯了
We found Reynolds.

876
01:00:07,781 --> 01:00:10,833
當趕到時太遲了
Moments too late, from what I hear.

877
01:00:10,876 --> 01:00:14,961
我必須打給他老婆 告訴她丈夫被活埋了
I had to call his wife and tell her that her husband had been buried alive.

878
01:00:15,002 --> 01:00:17,793
司法制度需要嚴厲，尼克
Justice should be harsh, Nick,

879
01:00:17,831 --> 01:00:20,486
尤其是對於那種對他人拒絕公正的人
but especially for those who denied it to others.

880
01:00:20,528 --> 01:00:23,183
殺你的牢友呢？怎麼回事？
And your cell-mate? What was that about?

881
01:00:26,817 --> 01:00:29,903
你殺死這人就是因為午餐來遲了
You murdered a man because your lunch was late.

882
01:00:29,946 --> 01:00:31,909
不
No.

883
01:00:31,943 --> 01:00:36,233
不，不，是你殺了他 因為你沒有信守承諾
No. No, you murdered him because you couldn't keep your word.

884
01:00:36,271 --> 01:00:39,629
我們達成了協議，你和我 下午1點
We made a deal, you and I: 00 PM.

885
01:00:39,665 --> 01:00:42,854
那是一個非常重要的原則 我希望你能開始學會，尼克
That's a pretty important principle I'd like you start learning, Nick:

886
01:00:42,894 --> 01:00:44,948
- 遵守你的諾言 - 哦，真的嗎？
- keeping your word. - Oh, really?

887
01:00:44,991 --> 01:00:47,975
當你折磨並殺死那些人時 你又在按什麼原則行事
What principle was at work when you tortured and killed those people?

888
01:00:48,018 --> 01:00:51,706
那就是每個人都應該為自己的行為負責
That everyone must be held accountable for their actions.

889
01:00:57,804 --> 01:01:00,707
你以為你的妻子女兒 對你以她們的名義殺人
You think your wife and daughter would feel good

890
01:01:00,757 --> 01:01:03,592
會感覺很好嗎？
about you killing in their name?

891
01:01:29,322 --> 01:01:32,943
我妻子和女兒再也沒有感覺了
My wife and daughter can't feeI anything.

892
01:01:34,248 --> 01:01:36,234
他們死了
They're dead.

893
01:02:12,203 --> 01:02:14,297
嘿，尼克
Hey, Nick?

894
01:02:14,330 --> 01:02:16,665
查克萊德的不動產一事 史坦菲德法官拒絕了我們
On Clyde's real estate, Judge Stansfield shut us down.

895
01:02:16,833 --> 01:02:20,293
他在尋找某個合法案例 我不知道是否存在
He's looking for some sort of legal precedent that I'm not sure exists.

896
01:02:20,461 --> 01:02:21,503
- 但？ - 但…
- But? - But...

897
01:02:21,671 --> 01:02:22,963
我想我可能找到了其它方法
I think I may have found a way around it.

898
01:02:23,130 --> 01:02:25,298
- 我要找一個朋友幫忙 - 你的朋友是誰？
- I'll call in a favor from a friend. - Who's your friend?

899
01:02:25,466 --> 01:02:27,634
不能透露朋友的名字 不然他們不會幫忙
You don't name your friends or they stop doing you favors.

900
01:02:27,802 --> 01:02:29,469
坎特雷爾還說了什麼
Something else Cantrell said.

901
01:02:29,637 --> 01:02:33,640
沒有，就這些了 喬納斯，你好
No, that was all you. Jonas, hi.

902
01:02:34,684 --> 01:02:37,769
她思考的模式和你一樣，尼克 我看你把她訓練得很不錯
She's thinking just like you, Nick. Guess you trained her well.

903
01:02:37,937 --> 01:02:40,939
- 有天她會坐上我的位子 - 我們透透氣去吧
- One day she'll have my job. - Let's get some air.

904
01:02:43,985 --> 01:02:46,319
克萊德的政府契約款困擾著我
Clyde's government contract payments were bothering me,

905
01:02:46,487 --> 01:02:49,072
因此我動用了一些舊關係 我們要見個人
so I pulled some ancient strings. We're meeting someone.

906
01:02:49,240 --> 01:02:50,699
會是誰呢？
Who might that be?

907
01:02:50,867 --> 01:02:54,703
那些做真正下流事情的人 所以我們才能夠住著美國夢
Someone who does some really nasty shit so we can live the American dream.

908
01:03:06,883 --> 01:03:08,842
那麼克萊德終於瘋了嗎？
So Clyde finally lost it?

909
01:03:09,010 --> 01:03:11,136
一定是有人真的惹毛他了
Somebody must have really pissed him off.

910
01:03:11,304 --> 01:03:13,638
你和謝爾頓一起工作過？對吧？
You worked with Shelton, is that right?

911
01:03:13,806 --> 01:03:17,517
首先，我從沒來過這裡 我們也從沒有對過話
Okay, first of all, I was never here and we never spoke.

912
01:03:17,685 --> 01:03:20,312
告訴我們在對付誰 謝爾頓是間諜還是…
Tell us what we're dealing with. Shelton was a spy or-

913
01:03:20,479 --> 01:03:23,064
間諜太稀鬆平常了 我就是間諜
Spies are a dime a dozen. I'm a spy.

914
01:03:23,232 --> 01:03:26,735
克萊德是天才 他是會動腦筋那個
Clyde is a brain. He's a think-tank type guy.

915
01:03:26,903 --> 01:03:29,404
他的專長是低速衝擊動力操作
His specialty was low-impact kinetic operations.

916
01:03:29,572 --> 01:03:31,948
這是他殺人一種美化的說法嗎？
Is this a hell of a fancy way to say that he kills people?

917
01:03:32,116 --> 01:03:33,241
我們殺人
We kill people.

918
01:03:33,409 --> 01:03:35,911
他可以不共處一室就能幹出來
He figured out how to do it without ever being in the same room.

919
01:03:36,078 --> 01:03:39,414
這是他的天賦，而且他是最優秀的
It was his gift, and he was the best.

920
01:03:39,582 --> 01:03:42,000
有次我們對付一個狡猾的目標
One time we're tasking this tricky target.

921
01:03:42,168 --> 01:03:44,669
我們用巡航導彈、猛禽戰機
I mean, we're using cruise missiles and predators

922
01:03:44,837 --> 01:03:48,632
甚至動用了B2隱形轟炸機 飛到這傢伙的別墅去炸他
and we even had a B-2 bomber flatten this guy's villa with a JDAM.

923
01:03:48,799 --> 01:03:50,425
我們循規蹈矩的方法浪費了數百萬
All right? We're burning up millions in ordnance

924
01:03:50,593 --> 01:03:51,927
連這傢伙的影子都沒有見到
and we're getting nowhere with this guy.

925
01:03:52,094 --> 01:03:55,013
所以我們找來了克萊德 請他解決這個問題
So we call Clyde and we ask him to solve our problem.

926
01:03:55,181 --> 01:03:57,098
克萊德發明一項高強力縫線
Clyde develops a Kevlar thread

927
01:03:57,266 --> 01:03:59,935
有著碳纖維制的高科技制輪裝置
with a high-tech ratchet made of carbon fiber

928
01:04:00,102 --> 01:04:01,978
能夠安裝在領帶裡
put in a necktie.

929
01:04:02,146 --> 01:04:04,731
兩天後，壞蛋太太回到家
Two days later, Mrs. Bad Guy comes home,

930
01:04:04,899 --> 01:04:07,609
發現壞蛋先生倒在浴室的瓷磚上
finds Mr. Bad Guy dead on the bathroom tile,

931
01:04:07,777 --> 01:04:09,110
窒息而死
choked to death.

932
01:04:10,905 --> 01:04:13,782
我所說的是，只能假設這傢伙可以
What I'm saying is, just assume that this guy can hear and see

933
01:04:13,950 --> 01:04:15,617
聽到或看到你的一舉一動
everything that you're doing.

934
01:04:15,785 --> 01:04:17,911
不，我們把他關起來了 高度戒備中
Nick: No, we've got him locked away, maximum security.

935
01:04:18,079 --> 01:04:21,081
如果他在監獄，那是因為他想在獄中
Man: If he's in jail, it's because he wants to be in jail.

936
01:04:21,248 --> 01:04:24,918
他是個天生的戰略家 他的每個行動都有意義
He's a born tactician. Every move that he makes, it means something.

937
01:04:25,962 --> 01:04:28,421
他殺死牢友，你以為是隨意的嗎？
That cell-mate that he killed- you think that was random?

938
01:04:30,049 --> 01:04:31,758
不是
No.

939
01:04:31,926 --> 01:04:34,552
那只是棋盤上被擺佈的一個棋子
That's a pawn being moved off the board.

940
01:04:36,138 --> 01:04:38,974
換作我，我會找出下一個目標
If I were you, I'd be looking for the next piece.

941
01:04:39,141 --> 01:04:41,810
和那案子有關聯的每個人
Anybody who had anything to do with that case,

942
01:04:41,978 --> 01:04:43,979
他不會放過你們的
he's gonna be coming after you.

943
01:04:44,981 --> 01:04:49,192
那你的意思是？ 你是說我們無法阻止他？
So what are you saying? You saying we can't stop him?

944
01:04:51,278 --> 01:04:54,114
走進他的牢房 給他腦袋一顆子彈
Walk into his cell and put a bullet in his head.

945
01:04:55,992 --> 01:04:58,952
除此之外？ 別無他法，你無法阻止他
Aside from that? No, you can't stop him.

946
01:04:59,120 --> 01:05:01,638
如果克萊德想要你死，你就死
If Clyde wants you dead, you're dead.

947
01:05:13,050 --> 01:05:16,052
- 你好 - 莎拉？莎拉，是尼克
- Hello? - Sarah? Sarah, it's Nick.

948
01:05:16,220 --> 01:05:17,971
安排和伯奇法官會個面
Set up a meeting with Judge Burch.

949
01:05:18,139 --> 01:05:20,140
我們得讓她幫我們把克萊德監押起來
We need her to help us keep Clyde on ice.

950
01:05:20,307 --> 01:05:22,934
幫我們做什麼？尼克 他已經在牢裡了
Help us with what, Nick? The man's in prison.

951
01:05:23,102 --> 01:05:24,811
他比我們想像的更可怕
He's worse than we thought.

952
01:05:24,979 --> 01:05:27,439
- 切斯特是你的男朋友，對吧？ - 切斯特
- Chester's your boyfriend, right? - Chester.

953
01:05:27,606 --> 01:05:29,441
是的
Yeah.

954
01:05:29,608 --> 01:05:32,819
很好，也許去他那待幾天
Good. Maybe stay a few days at his place.

955
01:05:32,987 --> 01:05:36,031
再叫唐尼派輛巡邏車到我家來
And have Dunnigan send a patroI car to my house.

956
01:05:36,198 --> 01:05:37,949
對此很抱歉，莎拉
Sorry about this, Sarah.

957
01:05:45,166 --> 01:05:47,417
我不能取代刑法
Judge Burch: I can't supersede the penal code.

958
01:05:47,585 --> 01:05:49,044
你們已經把他關入禁閉室
You've already got him in solitary.

959
01:05:49,211 --> 01:05:51,463
到下周隨便一個律師助理就會讓他出來
A half-decent paralegal will have him out of there by next week.

960
01:05:51,630 --> 01:05:53,298
我們只想限制他的選擇
We just want to limit his options;

961
01:05:53,466 --> 01:05:55,133
減少他的聯繫，減少渠道
give him less contact, less access,

962
01:05:55,316 --> 01:05:58,651
即使只是解除他一個星期的委託權
even if it's just rescinding his mandatory exercise period for a week.

963
01:05:58,688 --> 01:06:01,089
- 用什麼名義？ - 什麼都可以
- Under what cause? - Whatever cause you want.

964
01:06:01,125 --> 01:06:03,390
隨便用什麼法條
Wrap it around whatever piece of legal doctrine

965
01:06:03,429 --> 01:06:07,093
只要能合理化這個即可，法官大人
that helps you rationalize it, Your Honor.

966
01:06:08,736 --> 01:06:10,204
那麼，我直說吧
So let me get this straight:

967
01:06:10,238 --> 01:06:13,072
你們想要我侵犯上帝賦予他的權利？
you want me to violate his God-given civil rights

968
01:06:13,109 --> 01:06:15,874
以某種罪惡第六感的名義
in the name of some murky sense of the greater good.

969
01:06:15,913 --> 01:06:18,007
先生們，是這個意思嗎？
Is that the gist of it, gentlemen?

970
01:06:24,826 --> 01:06:27,387
好吧，我入伙
Okay. I'm game.

971
01:06:28,398 --> 01:06:32,529
只是別想持續太久，好嗎？
Just don't plan on it sticking for long, all right?

972
01:06:36,075 --> 01:06:37,805
等會，你要接電話？
Wait, you're gonna take that,

973
01:06:37,845 --> 01:06:40,007
你訓斥過我接電話的事情
after all the grief you've given me over cell phones?

974
01:06:40,048 --> 01:06:43,280
那是當法官的好處之一，瑞斯先生
That's one of the benefits of being a judge, Mr. Rice.

975
01:06:43,319 --> 01:06:46,346
我相當可以隨心所欲
I can pretty much do whatever I want.

976
01:06:48,726 --> 01:06:50,194
喂？
Hello?

977
01:06:52,732 --> 01:06:54,530
哦，上帝
Oh my God.

978
01:06:54,568 --> 01:06:57,231
退後，退後
Nick: Back out. Back out.

979
01:07:00,032 --> 01:07:03,993
…在市政廳，儘管還無法證實這些細節
Female reporter:... at city hall, though we are unable to confirm the details,

980
01:07:04,161 --> 01:07:06,287
但我們知道至少一人死亡
we do know that at least one person is dead

981
01:07:06,455 --> 01:07:08,581
官方稱很可能是謀殺
in what officials are calling a possible murder.

982
01:07:08,749 --> 01:07:11,000
我們會有記者繼續…
We have reporters on the ground...

983
01:07:11,168 --> 01:07:12,418
上來
Up.

984
01:07:17,508 --> 01:07:19,342
有人在幫這傢伙
Somebody's helping this guy-

985
01:07:19,510 --> 01:07:21,761
手機裡的炸彈 而她毫不知情
a bomb in that phone, and she doesn't know about it.

986
01:07:21,929 --> 01:07:24,889
誰能做到呢？
Who had access?

987
01:07:25,057 --> 01:07:26,766
你還好嗎？
Are you okay?

988
01:07:26,934 --> 01:07:29,602
我是戰爭裡過來的，還有兩個前妻 我沒事的
I've survived the war and two ex-wives. I'll be fine.

989
01:07:31,605 --> 01:07:33,439
你還好嗎？
How are you holding up?

990
01:07:33,607 --> 01:07:35,900
我還好
I'm good.

991
01:07:51,667 --> 01:07:53,794
現在你把法官也殺了？
So you're killing judges now?

992
01:07:53,836 --> 01:07:58,034
以我的經驗來看，尼克 只有血的教訓才能持久
In my experience, Nick, lessons not learned in blood are soon forgotten.

993
01:07:58,073 --> 01:08:00,872
復仇能讓你在晚上得到溫暖嗎
And vengeance keeps you warm at night.

994
01:08:00,910 --> 01:08:02,707
復仇？
Vengeance?

995
01:08:04,547 --> 01:08:07,573
這就是你所認為的嗎？復仇？
That's what you think this is about? Vengeance?

996
01:08:07,617 --> 01:08:09,448
還會是什麼呢？
What else could it be?

997
01:08:09,485 --> 01:08:13,786
不，尼克，我有10年的時間可以復仇 如果我要做的話
No, Nick, I had 10 years for vengeance, if that's what I wanted.

998
01:08:13,824 --> 01:08:17,624
你沒意識到我每天早上八點看你上班？
You don't think that I watch you go to work every morning at 8:00 AM?

999
01:08:17,661 --> 01:08:21,688
或者看著凱莉帶丹尼斯8點15去上學？
Or that I watch Kelly take Denise to schooI, 8:15?

1000
01:08:21,732 --> 01:08:25,634
不，我可以在任何時候毀了你和你的家庭
No, I could have slaughtered you or your family anytime I wanted!

1001
01:08:25,669 --> 01:08:28,537
你甚至想過碰我的家人…
You even think about touching my family-

1002
01:08:28,573 --> 01:08:32,202
你甚至想過碰我的家人…
you even think about touching my family...

1003
01:08:40,486 --> 01:08:43,011
我是做我的工作
I do my job.

1004
01:08:43,055 --> 01:08:45,455
我是做的最出色的
I'm the best at it.

1005
01:08:45,491 --> 01:08:47,982
- 做的不錯 - 你在做你的工作？
- It works. - You were doing yourjob

1006
01:08:48,027 --> 01:08:52,361
以對你有利的方式，尼克 對你有利的方式
the way that best served you, Nick- the way that best served you.

1007
01:08:52,398 --> 01:08:55,698
- 這點得改變了 - 你想怎樣，克萊德？
- That has to change. - What do you want, Clyde?

1008
01:08:55,736 --> 01:08:58,466
你在和整個世界作戰？ 這不會令任何人退卻
You at war with the whole world? It's not gonna bring anybody back.

1009
01:08:58,505 --> 01:09:01,732
不，我在和這個…
No, I'm at war with this-

1010
01:09:01,775 --> 01:09:04,703
這個…這個破爛的玩意作戰
this- this broken thing-

1011
01:09:04,745 --> 01:09:07,372
把你和我連在一起的玩意
this thing that brought you and I together.

1012
01:09:07,414 --> 01:09:10,043
這爛玩意對神經正常的人有用
This broken thing works for people that are sane.

1013
01:09:10,084 --> 01:09:12,484
你以為你在做的事情能夠改變任何事情嗎？
You think doing what you're doing is gonna change anything?

1014
01:09:12,520 --> 01:09:15,216
你和其它幫助你的人
You and whoever else you have helping you

1015
01:09:15,256 --> 01:09:17,247
都要付出代價
are gonna pay.

1016
01:09:18,993 --> 01:09:23,795
我認為你並不知道誰在幫我 或我在做什麼？
I don't think you have any idea who's helping me or what I'm doing.

1017
01:09:23,832 --> 01:09:25,163
遲早的事
It's a matter of time.

1018
01:09:25,200 --> 01:09:27,532
看，你看過屍體 你見到煙霧
See, you see the bodies, you see the smoke,

1019
01:09:27,569 --> 01:09:30,697
可還有更大的場面等著你
but the larger picture still eludes you.

1020
01:09:30,739 --> 01:09:32,866
說說看
Do tell.

1021
01:09:34,043 --> 01:09:37,275
我很想說…
I would like to...

1022
01:09:37,314 --> 01:09:39,179
但我選擇演給你看
but I would rather show you.

1023
01:09:41,251 --> 01:09:45,347
我仍然對你有信念 所以我會給你最後一次機會
I still have faith in you, so I'm gonna give you one last chance.

1024
01:09:45,388 --> 01:09:46,753
這交易是
Here's the deal:

1025
01:09:46,790 --> 01:09:51,421
釋放我，並在早上六點前撤銷所有的指控
release me and drop all charges by 6:00 AM.

1026
01:09:51,462 --> 01:09:54,260
- 早上六點，尼克 - 不然怎樣？
- 6:00 AM, Nick. - Or what?

1027
01:09:56,834 --> 01:09:59,701
不然我殺了每個人
Or I kill everyone.

1028
01:10:11,015 --> 01:10:12,941
- 你好？ - 莎拉
- Hello? - Nick: Yeah, Sarah,

1029
01:10:12,977 --> 01:10:16,114
他一定有同夥 可能就是牢裡的某個人
he has to have an accomplice- probably somebody inside the prison.

1030
01:10:16,156 --> 01:10:19,570
我們必須調查所有犯人的檔案 看能否找出某種關聯
We have to go through all the prisoners' files to find some sort of connection.

1031
01:10:19,608 --> 01:10:21,499
檔案要送到辦公室嗎？
Do you want the files brought to the office?

1032
01:10:21,536 --> 01:10:24,881
不，沒時間了 叫大家一起到監獄來
No, there isn't time. Get everybody together and bring them to the prison.

1033
01:10:24,918 --> 01:10:26,464
我們要進駐
We're moving in.

1034
01:10:44,912 --> 01:10:47,034
別再看表了
Stop looking at your watch.

1035
01:10:49,276 --> 01:10:51,098
你朋友那邊有消息嗎？
Anything from your friend?

1036
01:10:51,138 --> 01:10:52,960
與巴拿馬那邊的條款很棘手
This treaty with Panama is a mess.

1037
01:10:52,998 --> 01:10:55,592
我們無法得到任何有關財產持有的記錄
We can't access anything about specific property holdings,

1038
01:10:55,642 --> 01:10:57,636
不過我朋友發現了一個後門
but my friend found this tiny loophole

1039
01:10:57,686 --> 01:11:01,015
可以瀏覽克萊德公司開銷記錄
that grants us access to Clyde's corporate expenses.

1040
01:11:01,065 --> 01:11:03,178
有用麼？
Does that help?

1041
01:11:06,904 --> 01:11:10,941
那麼對比下費城出售過的工業資產價格
So we match sale prices of industrial properties sold in Philly

1042
01:11:10,991 --> 01:11:13,819
和他公司所購買過的物品金額
up against purchases made by his corporation.

1043
01:11:13,869 --> 01:11:18,088
我知道了
Okay, I got it.

1044
01:11:25,923 --> 01:11:29,862
- 嘿，尼克，我能問你點事嗎？ - 嗯？
- Hey, Nick, can I ask you something? - Hmm?

1045
01:11:31,887 --> 01:11:34,214
你現在會做同樣的選擇嗎？
Would you do it the same way now?

1046
01:11:34,264 --> 01:11:37,820
你仍會幫多比達成協議嗎？
Would you still cut a deal for Darby?

1047
01:11:38,602 --> 01:11:42,598
這是工作呀，莎拉 我們得做出選擇
This is the job, Sarah. We have to make choices.

1048
01:11:42,648 --> 01:11:47,732
- 但你做出正確選擇了嗎？ - 我們的選擇正確，對吧？
- But did you make the right choice? - We made the right choice, right?

1049
01:11:49,029 --> 01:11:51,440
我不知道
I don't know.

1050
01:11:51,490 --> 01:11:54,026
我35歲了，尼克
I'm 35, Nick.

1051
01:11:54,076 --> 01:11:56,153
有許多東西…許多的可能性 
And there are things- there are possibilities

1052
01:11:56,203 --> 01:11:57,954
是我現在無法擁有的
that I'm not gonna have now.

1053
01:11:59,123 --> 01:12:03,042
沒關係，我知道這是交易的一部分
And it's okay. I know it's part of the deal.

1054
01:12:04,878 --> 01:12:08,047
別誤會我 我喜歡為你工作
And don't get me wrong. I love working for you.

1055
01:12:12,594 --> 01:12:15,054
但我只想弄清楚我放棄的那些東西
But I just want to make sure I gave up those things

1056
01:12:15,222 --> 01:12:18,641
不光是為了高定罪率
for more than just a high conviction rate.

1057
01:12:38,537 --> 01:12:40,329
你要喝咖啡嗎？
Do you want any more coffee?

1058
01:12:40,497 --> 01:12:41,747
不
No.

1059
01:13:37,679 --> 01:13:39,931
好了
All right.

1060
01:13:40,098 --> 01:13:42,433
好了，我們集中精神 這人不是神僊
All right, let's just get focused here. This guy's not God.

1061
01:13:42,601 --> 01:13:45,019
他不是萬能的 他只是準備充分而已
He's not the All Powerful. He's just well-prepared.

1062
01:13:45,187 --> 01:13:47,188
我們也需要準備充分
We need to be equally well-prepared.

1063
01:13:47,356 --> 01:13:51,067
回家休息一兩個小時 然後回來重新開始
Take a couple of hours, go home, come back. We'll get a fresh start.

1064
01:13:51,235 --> 01:13:52,610
好嗎？
Okay?

1065
01:14:02,621 --> 01:14:06,457
過來，老人家 看我們能否給你買到早餐
Man: Come on, old man, let's see if we can find you some breakfast.

1066
01:14:21,306 --> 01:14:23,558
嘿，尼克，去休息一會吧
Hey, Nick, get some rest.

1067
01:14:23,725 --> 01:14:28,062
待我問候切斯特 我幾時才能見到他？
Give Chester my regards. When do I get to meet him?

1068
01:14:28,230 --> 01:14:31,482
哦，還不到那個時候
Oh, he's not ready for that.

1069
01:14:32,734 --> 01:14:34,277
晚安，瓊納斯
'Night, Jonas.

1070
01:14:45,622 --> 01:14:47,873
我不知道這個案子的結果會怎樣，尼克
I don't know how this one's gonna turn out, Nick.

1071
01:14:48,041 --> 01:14:50,042
我們得阻止他 那就是結果
We're gonna stop him. That's how it's gonna turn out.

1072
01:14:51,432 --> 01:14:53,011
啊！
Ahh!

1073
01:15:00,938 --> 01:15:02,149
啊！

1074
01:15:02,306 --> 01:15:05,016
莎拉
Sarah.

1075
01:15:10,647 --> 01:15:12,106
莎拉
Sarah.

1076
01:15:45,515 --> 01:15:49,046
在過去的48個小時中 6名司法部的官員
Reporter: In the past 48 hours, six officials from the Justice Department

1077
01:15:49,227 --> 01:15:52,521
死於一連串的有預謀的襲擊中
have been killed in a series of vicious and premeditated attacks.

1078
01:15:52,689 --> 01:15:55,358
這還是美國歷史上的第一次
This marks the first time in the history of the United States

1079
01:15:55,525 --> 01:16:00,529
很顯然政府官員在被系統性地謀殺
where government officials have been, by all appearances,systematically murdered.

1080
01:16:00,697 --> 01:16:03,532
我們會繼續跟進事件的發展 為你帶來最新最細的報道…
We'll continue to follow this story and bring you up-to-the-minute details...

1081
01:16:07,537 --> 01:16:10,539
尼克，很抱歉我現在不得不這樣做 但我們在這裡找到了些東西
Nick, I'm sorry to have to do this now, but we've got something here.

1082
01:16:10,700 --> 01:16:13,570
就在牆外發現了這個…
Found this right outside the wall-

1083
01:16:13,606 --> 01:16:15,542
無線電裝置
radio beacon-

1084
01:16:15,577 --> 01:16:18,242
當人通過大門時 發送信號給車上的炸彈
sent an arming signal to the car bombs when they went through the gate.

1085
01:16:18,282 --> 01:16:21,049
警衛說他們抵達這前 檢查過每一輛車
Dunnigan: Security said they checked every car before anybody got in them.

1086
01:16:21,088 --> 01:16:24,619
他們沒有檢查油箱 大概那些奸鳥會放那裡
They didn't check the gas tanks. That's where the clever prick put 'em.

1087
01:16:24,662 --> 01:16:26,325
也是個精密的玩意
Real precise stuff too.

1088
01:16:26,366 --> 01:16:28,598
如果他想，可以幹掉更多的人
Could have taken out a lot more if he wanted to.

1089
01:16:28,637 --> 01:16:31,370
- 尼克的車呢？ - 怪就怪在這裡
- Cantrell: What about Nick's car? - That's the weird thing.

1090
01:16:31,409 --> 01:16:34,074
他的車子沒問題 沒被做過手腳
It's clean- hadn't been touched.

1091
01:16:35,284 --> 01:16:37,277
我得走了
I gotta go.

1092
01:16:45,138 --> 01:16:47,074
天呀
Woman: Jesus Christ.

1093
01:16:55,393 --> 01:16:57,727
請迴避下
Privacy, please.

1094
01:16:59,367 --> 01:17:02,498
那讓我直說吧
So let me get this straight:

1095
01:17:02,540 --> 01:17:05,569
我們不光知道誰幹的
not only do we know who did it,

1096
01:17:05,613 --> 01:17:09,884
而且我們把他關起來了 可是他仍舊在殺人？
we have him locked up and he's still killing people?

1097
01:17:11,191 --> 01:17:15,428
你們這些人一定把這案子搞砸了
You boys sure fucked this one up.

1098
01:17:15,467 --> 01:17:19,635
媒體會弄死我們的
The press is gonna kill us.

1099
01:17:19,675 --> 01:17:21,669
有人能給我解釋一下嗎？
Can someone explain this to me?

1100
01:17:21,714 --> 01:17:23,273
暫時不能
We can't yet.

1101
01:17:28,694 --> 01:17:32,065
你怎麼還像安然無事一樣，喬納斯
How did this get away from you, Jonas?

1102
01:17:32,102 --> 01:17:34,368
說來複雜，埃普麗爾
It's complicated, April.

1103
01:17:34,406 --> 01:17:37,037
他非常狡猾 他非常憤怒
He's very smart. He's very angry.

1104
01:17:37,078 --> 01:17:39,675
我們估計有同夥在外面幫助他
We assume he has an accomplice helping him on the outside.

1105
01:17:39,717 --> 01:17:43,521
我不要這種談話
I'm not having this conversation.

1106
01:17:43,558 --> 01:17:47,191
我不關心他有多聰明 或者是誰在幫他
I don't care how smart he is or who's helping him.

1107
01:17:52,911 --> 01:17:56,510
我們將發佈聲明說我們抓到了嫌犯 我們正在追查線索…
We'll release a statement saying we have suspects, we're following leads-

1108
01:17:56,552 --> 01:17:59,649
- 無需驚慌 - 市長，我向你保證
- nothing alarming. - Mayor, you have my word,

1109
01:17:59,691 --> 01:18:03,654
我們會阻止這傢伙的 他不會再傷害任何人
we are gonna stop this guy. He's not gonna hurt anybody else.

1110
01:18:08,409 --> 01:18:11,176
現在開始我給你們每個人加強保安
I'm assigning security to each of you from now on.

1111
01:18:15,457 --> 01:18:18,020
控制住局勢，先生們
Get this situation under control, gentlemen.

1112
01:18:34,142 --> 01:18:36,352
爸爸？
Dad?

1113
01:18:36,520 --> 01:18:38,854
我打賭你不記得我做的那個
I bet you don't remember when I did that.

1114
01:18:39,022 --> 01:18:41,440
我打賭我記得
I bet you I do.

1115
01:18:56,456 --> 01:18:58,249
怎麼了？
What?

1116
01:18:58,416 --> 01:19:00,125
沒什麼
Nothing.

1117
01:19:00,293 --> 01:19:03,587
你和你媽媽要度幾天假
You and your mother are going away on a little vacation, that's all.

1118
01:19:03,755 --> 01:19:05,339
- 你喜歡假期，對吧？ - 是啊
- You like vacations, right? - Yeah.

1119
01:19:05,507 --> 01:19:07,383
好
Good.

1120
01:19:07,551 --> 01:19:09,260
可為什麼？
But why?

1121
01:19:09,427 --> 01:19:11,595
為什麼不現在去？
Why not now?

1122
01:19:11,763 --> 01:19:13,931
好的
Okay.

1123
01:19:14,099 --> 01:19:16,934
不需要理由，對吧？
Don't need an excuse, right?

1124
01:19:20,480 --> 01:19:21,772
好吧
All right.

1125
01:19:21,940 --> 01:19:25,901
別用電話，別用信用卡，別用電腦 只能用現金
No phone calls, no credit cards, no computers- just cash.

1126
