- 該死 - 那是你家嗎？
- Shit. - Is that your house?

1293
01:37:47,586 --> 01:37:50,421
是的
Yes.

1294
01:37:51,423 --> 01:37:53,883
寶貝，告訴我你們沒事
Baby, please tell me you're okay.

1295
01:37:54,051 --> 01:37:55,510
丹尼斯，她在哪？
Denise- where is she?

1296
01:37:55,678 --> 01:37:57,387
她跟你在一起？ 你確定？
Is she with you? Are you sure?

1297
01:37:57,554 --> 01:37:59,305
好
Okay.

1298
01:37:59,473 --> 01:38:01,933
待著別動 我一會再解釋
Stay where you are. I'll explain later.

1299
01:38:02,101 --> 01:38:03,935
我愛你
I love you.

1300
01:38:10,946 --> 01:38:13,855
（取得勝利就要重兵集結在 所有權力活動中心--敵人的重心）

1301
01:38:13,946 --> 01:38:16,155
馮·克勞塞維茨
Nick: Von Clausewitz.

1302
01:38:20,661 --> 01:38:22,203
看看那個
Look at that.

1303
01:38:29,586 --> 01:38:31,379
他在市政廳
He's at City Hall.

1304
01:38:32,881 --> 01:38:34,924
你可以走了，先生
You're free to go, sir.

1305
01:38:35,092 --> 01:38:38,094
- 抱歉造成不便，先生 - 不用，沒關係
- Sorry for the inconvenience, sir. - No, don't worry about it.

1306
01:38:39,513 --> 01:38:42,140
安全要比抱歉重要，是吧？
Better to be safe than sorry, right?

1307
01:38:43,600 --> 01:38:45,643
準備疏散大樓
Dunnigan: Get ready to evacuate the building.

1308
01:38:45,811 --> 01:38:47,812
我們需要一支戰術小隊和防爆小組
We'll need a tactical unit and a bomb squad.

1309
01:38:47,980 --> 01:38:49,230
壞主意，叫他們悄悄進去
Bad idea. Have them come in soft.

1310
01:38:49,398 --> 01:38:52,066
如果謝爾頓認出我或我們中任何一個人 事情就糟糕了
If Shelton spots them or any of us, we're fucked.

1311
01:39:15,841 --> 01:39:18,134
嘿
Hey.

1312
01:39:20,679 --> 01:39:22,305
- 戰術小隊在哪？ - 正趕來
- Where's the tactical team? - En route.

1313
01:39:22,473 --> 01:39:24,682
- 他們悄悄地過來，不鳴警笛 - 拆彈部隊呢？
- They're coming in soft- no sirens. - Bomb squad?

1314
01:39:24,850 --> 01:39:26,392
你正在看著呢
You're looking at it.

1315
01:39:26,560 --> 01:39:29,854
對，那我們走北邊樓梯 你走西邊
Right, okay. We take the north surge; you take the west.

1316
01:39:30,022 --> 01:39:31,439
我們再聯繫
We'll call.

1317
01:39:36,487 --> 01:39:38,071
- 喔，喔，喔 - 請出示證件
- Whoa whoa whoa whoa. - IDs, please.

1318
01:39:38,238 --> 01:39:40,656
- 他是地區檢察官 - 很不錯，麻煩出示證件
- He's the fucking DA. - Good for him. IDs, please.

1319
01:39:40,824 --> 01:39:42,825
今晚這裡怎麼回事
What's going on here tonight?

1320
01:39:42,993 --> 01:39:45,203
- 所有高層在這開安保會議 - 哪一層？
- Security meeting with all the brass. - What floor?

1321
01:39:45,370 --> 01:39:47,288
六樓…會議室
6th floor- caucus room.

1322
01:39:50,209 --> 01:39:53,961
- 這是幾樓？ - 那是五樓，先生
- What floor is this? - That's the 5th floor, sir.

1323
01:39:54,129 --> 01:39:56,172
正好是高層會議室的下面
Directly below the caucus room.

1324
01:39:56,340 --> 01:40:00,093
如果我們發現混蛋正在作案 我們要抓活的
You catch this motherfucker red-handed, we gotta take him alive.

1325
01:40:22,199 --> 01:40:24,033
他在哪？
Where is he?

1326
01:40:24,201 --> 01:40:26,786
我們到底在找什麼？
What the fuck are we looking for?

1327
01:40:26,954 --> 01:40:29,038
等等，等等
Wait wait wait.

1328
01:40:29,206 --> 01:40:30,414
在那
Right there.

1329
01:40:30,582 --> 01:40:33,292
退後，別碰任何東西
Garza: Stand back. Don't touch anything.

1330
01:40:34,586 --> 01:40:37,338
那絕對不是我的第一感覺
It wasn't exactly my first instinct.

1331
01:41:16,336 --> 01:41:18,337
麻煩給我看看證件
Can I see your ID, please?

1332
01:41:25,387 --> 01:41:27,763
好了，下一輛，往前走
All right, next car, pull forward!

1333
01:42:02,299 --> 01:42:05,843
爆炸物
Garza: Malglinite.

1334
01:42:06,011 --> 01:42:08,512
那是凝固汽油彈 這鬼東西基本上會炸跨整層樓
That's napalm, basically. This shit'll take out the entire floor

1335
01:42:08,680 --> 01:42:10,514
和這層上方的樓層
and the one above us.

1336
01:42:10,682 --> 01:42:14,685
看起來…好像是由這支手機所觸發
Looks like it's- looks like it's triggered by this cell phone here.

1337
01:42:14,853 --> 01:42:18,981
什麼？一來電話就激活了？
What? So an incoming call arms it?

1338
01:42:19,149 --> 01:42:23,110
是的，也許30秒就爆炸了
Yeah. Maybe 30 seconds till boom time.

1339
01:42:24,112 --> 01:42:26,405
- 天呀 - 唐尼根，你在幹嘛
- Jesus. - Dunnigan, what are you doing?

1340
01:42:26,573 --> 01:42:28,241
- 我要打給市長的保安人員 - 不行
- I'm calling the mayor's security. - We can't.

1341
01:42:28,408 --> 01:42:31,786
克萊德在盯著 如果他看見他們疏散，他會引爆的
Clyde is watching. He sees him evacuate and he will detonate this thing.

1342
01:42:31,954 --> 01:42:34,580
我們不能向市長透露
We don't tell the mayor anything.

1343
01:42:37,167 --> 01:42:39,335
那我們該怎麼做？
So what do we do?

1344
01:42:49,680 --> 01:42:51,347
等一下
Man: Wait a second.

1345
01:42:51,515 --> 01:42:53,391
來了
We've got something.

1346
01:42:53,558 --> 01:42:55,393
他要停下了
Man over radio: He's pulling up.

1347
01:43:17,541 --> 01:43:19,583
市長埃普麗爾·亨利
Man: Mayor April Henry.

1348
01:43:29,177 --> 01:43:31,846
感謝各位的匆忙趕來
Thank you for coming in on short notice.

1349
01:43:38,562 --> 01:43:40,021
我有一個簡單的問題
Mayor: I have one simple question.

1350
01:43:42,482 --> 01:43:45,484
為什麼克萊德·謝爾頓還在我的城市？
Why is Clyde Shelton still in my city?

1351
01:43:47,446 --> 01:43:49,572
我現在拒絕相信
Now I refuse to believe

1352
01:43:49,740 --> 01:43:54,160
這個人比國土安全部
that one man is smarter than Homeland Security,

1353
01:43:54,328 --> 01:43:58,748
FBI，行政司法長官或費城警察還聰明
the FBl, the sheriff's department, or Philly PD.

1354
01:43:58,915 --> 01:44:01,167
我不管我們怎麼做
I don't care how we do it, or what kind

1355
01:44:01,335 --> 01:44:04,587
或者必須啟動哪種的晦澀的司法程序
of obscure legaI justification we have to invoke, gentlemen.

1356
01:44:04,755 --> 01:44:07,798
先生們，我不在乎我們要遵守哪條法律
I don't care what laws we have to bend.

1357
01:44:07,966 --> 01:44:11,886
但我相信國土安全法案會有一個條款
I am sure that there is a provision of the Homeland Security Act

1358
01:44:12,054 --> 01:44:14,638
是我們可以啟動的
that we can activate.

1359
01:44:14,806 --> 01:44:17,933
明天之前將他趕出這裡
Just get him out of here by tomorrow.

1360
01:44:24,649 --> 01:44:26,150
克萊德？
Nick: Clyde?

1361
01:44:30,530 --> 01:44:32,782
尼克
Nick.

1362
01:44:32,949 --> 01:44:34,867
我沒料到還會有人陪我
I wasn't expecting company.

1363
01:44:38,288 --> 01:44:41,415
嗯，早知道就先稍微打掃一下
Yeah, I would have- I would have cleaned up a little.

1364
01:44:41,583 --> 01:44:44,377
從未見過任何人挖隧道到監獄
Never seen anybody tunnel into prison before.

1365
01:44:50,175 --> 01:44:54,136
被關進禁閉室的法子很聰明
And the solitary confinement? That was clever.

1366
01:44:54,304 --> 01:44:56,639
嗯，那正是贏家的玩法
Well, that's how winners play.

1367
01:44:56,807 --> 01:44:59,975
我們要讓其他人信服 他做的每一步都是正確的
We convince the other guy he's making all the right moves.

1368
01:45:00,977 --> 01:45:03,479
那你抓住我同夥了嗎？
So did you ever catch my accomplice?

1369
01:45:03,647 --> 01:45:05,314
是的，當然
Yeah, I did.

1370
01:45:05,482 --> 01:45:07,858
現在是你的末路了
It's the end of the road for you now.

1371
01:45:12,280 --> 01:45:14,865
你玩弄了我們，克萊德 你真的耍得我們團團轉
You played us, Clyde. You played us real good.

1372
01:45:15,033 --> 01:45:16,909
謝謝
Thank you.

1373
01:45:17,077 --> 01:45:20,121
知道麼，很高興你終於能夠賞識
You know, I'm glad you finally get to appreciate

1374
01:45:20,288 --> 01:45:22,206
我所做的這一切努力了
some of the effort that I put into all of this.

1375
01:45:22,374 --> 01:45:24,625
你特別想強調某點，克萊德
Well, you set out to make a point, Clyde.

1376
01:45:24,793 --> 01:45:25,876
你做到了
You made it.

1377
01:45:26,044 --> 01:45:27,753
不，人們仍然不懂
No, people still don't get it.

1378
01:45:27,921 --> 01:45:31,674
他們不重視我試圖說的 尼克，不過很快地他們就會了
They don't appreciate what I'm trying to say, Nick, but they will soon enough.

1379
01:45:31,842 --> 01:45:33,717
我關心過的一個人曾告訴過我
A man I cared about once told me

1380
01:45:33,885 --> 01:45:36,053
我們不能撤回我們已做了的決定
that we can't retract the decisions that we've made,

1381
01:45:36,221 --> 01:45:38,764
我們只能影響今後我們要做的決定
we can only affect the decisions we're going to make from here.

1382
01:45:38,932 --> 01:45:41,725
- 現在你想拯救我嗎，尼克？ - 我在給你一條出路
- Are you trying to save me now, Nick? - I'm giving you a way out.

1383
01:45:41,893 --> 01:45:43,519
差別很大
Big difference.

1384
01:45:43,687 --> 01:45:45,771
站在你一直在宣揚的那些立場上
Stand up for those principles you've been preaching.

1385
01:45:45,939 --> 01:45:49,525
所以你看我們都要負責 克萊德，包括你在內
See, we're all held accountable, Clyde. That includes you.

1386
01:45:49,693 --> 01:45:51,360
為何不做正確的事呢？
Why don't we do the right thing here?

1387
01:45:52,362 --> 01:45:54,864
我是在做正確的事，尼克
I'm doing the right thing, Nick.

1388
01:45:56,867 --> 01:45:58,534
你只需以那種方式去看
You just have to see it that way.

1389
01:45:58,702 --> 01:46:00,077
靠著謀殺那些人
By murdering all those people,

1390
01:46:00,245 --> 01:46:03,080
你的所作所為只會摧毀你對女兒的記憶
all you're doing is destroying the memory of your daughter

1391
01:46:03,248 --> 01:46:06,792
也會對很多人造成你正遭受的痛苦
and causing the same pain that you're suffering from.

1392
01:46:13,508 --> 01:46:17,928
那麼你有何建議呢，尼克？ 再做另一次交易嗎？
So what do you suggest, Nick? Make another deaI?

1393
01:46:18,096 --> 01:46:21,182
提最後一次條件？ 是那樣子嗎？
One finaI offer? Is that what it is?

1394
01:46:24,144 --> 01:46:27,813
我不再與殺人兇手做交易了，克萊德
I don't make deals with murderers anymore, Clyde.

1395
01:46:27,981 --> 01:46:29,982
你教我的
You taught me that.

1396
01:46:34,529 --> 01:46:38,240
終於
Finally.

1397
01:46:40,410 --> 01:46:42,995
幹得好，好極了
Well done. Bravo.

1398
01:46:43,163 --> 01:46:46,123
也許我並非是個很糟的老師
Maybe I wasn't such a bad teacher after all.

1399
01:46:46,291 --> 01:46:48,501
如果你幹這事，克萊德 這個決定
If you go through with this, Clyde, it's a decision

1400
01:46:48,668 --> 01:46:51,253
你後半輩子都要承受這個決定
you'll have to live with for the rest of your life.

1401
01:47:15,111 --> 01:47:16,987
對不起，尼克
I'm sorry, Nick.

1402
01:47:19,658 --> 01:47:21,575
我也是
Me too.

1403
01:47:31,753 --> 01:47:33,629
如我說過的，克萊德
Like I said, Clyde,

1404
01:47:33,797 --> 01:47:36,757
你後半輩子都要承受這個決定
it's a decision you'll have to live with for the rest of your life,

1405
01:47:36,925 --> 01:47:40,261
我想現在大概還剩25秒鐘吧？
which I figure by now is about 25 more seconds.

1406
01:50:46,925 --> 01:50:55,261
謝謝觀賞

1407
01:51:10,305 --> 01:51:12,848
「未曾見一夜」
# Ain't seen a night #

1408
01:51:13,016 --> 01:51:15,684
「雲開月明」
# Things work out right #

1409
01:51:15,852 --> 01:51:19,229
「消逝」
# Go by #

1410
01:51:21,357 --> 01:51:23,734
「心中成大事」
# Things on my mind #

1411
01:51:23,902 --> 01:51:26,361
「然時不我待」
# And I just don't have the time #

1412
01:51:26,529 --> 01:51:29,990
「似物是人非」
# And it don't seem right #

1413
01:51:32,744 --> 01:51:34,828
「未見有時」
# Ain't seen a day #

1414
01:51:34,996 --> 01:51:37,790
「斯人已無言」
# That I don't hear people say #

1415
01:51:37,957 --> 01:51:41,043
「自知人之將去」
# They know they're gonna die #

1416
01:51:44,088 --> 01:51:46,965
《守法公民》 「此事已成瘋癲」
# This may seem a little bit crazy #

1417
01:51:47,133 --> 01:51:51,345
「然斯人亦當勤勉」
# But I don't think you should be so lazy #

1418
01:51:55,350 --> 01:51:57,810
「似曾相識處」
# If you think you've heard this before #

1419
01:51:57,977 --> 01:51:59,812
「飲酒至闌珊」
# Well, stick around #

1420
01:51:59,979 --> 01:52:03,690
「盡其詳」
# I'm gonna tell you more #

1421
01:53:30,278 --> 01:53:33,113
「吾等皆草民」
# One just like the other #

1422
01:53:33,281 --> 01:53:35,240
「惡善伴行生」
# Sin's a good man's brother #

1423
01:53:35,408 --> 01:53:39,119
「知否？」
# But is that right? #

1424
01:53:41,539 --> 01:53:44,041
「汝知此不可為」
# You tell me that I don't #

1425
01:53:44,208 --> 01:53:46,418
「吾遂不為」
# Then I say I won't #

1426
01:53:46,586 --> 01:53:50,339
「然尚可為」
# But then I might #

1427
01:53:53,051 --> 01:53:55,761
「此行或可眾人期」
# You said this is the way it's supposed to be #

1428
01:53:55,929 --> 01:53:58,430
「卻吾念甚篤」
# But it just don't seem right to me #

1429
01:53:58,598 --> 01:54:02,559
「且視而不見」
# And that's outta sight #

1430
01:54:04,145 --> 01:54:07,064
「民教重於天」
# Some folks need an education #

1431
01:54:07,231 --> 01:54:11,610
「棄之國將不國」
# Don't give up or we'll lose the nation #

1432
01:54:15,531 --> 01:54:18,283
「天下之變」
# You say we need a revolution? #

1433
01:54:18,451 --> 01:54:19,785
「仿若」
# It seems to be #

1434
01:54:19,953 --> 01:54:23,914
「唯此一解矣」
# The only solution. #
